ygData.messageBody:
Journeyman's boots are the booties ye be speaking of. Tis a quest. The boots
will give you a form of level 9ish or so Spirit of the Wolf (SoW gets faster
as the caster goes up in levels, the JBoots sow is slower than 99% of the
SoWs you'll get from players, but faster than 95% of the mobs in the game).

Quest is long and hard, and ye need to be atleast 30th level to do it in a
group in SRo, or 40ish level in OOT. Read the spoiler around on various web
sites, like EQ'Lizer.

Froglok totem, if your on this list, should have been explained over several
times. Don't know what ye mean with thequestion is it like the water crystal
staff. Only thing similar between the two is that they are both LORE items
(can only have one at a time).

-Leod, 52nd Circle Shaman
-Dysin, 31st Circle Enchanter
